ing: 8 (1/2-inch) cubes Parmesan cheese, or to taste
n: Chicken Caesar Salad on a Stick
des: "This chicken Caesar-on-a-stick appetizer is a fun twist on a classic salad!"
ins: Thread a crouton, romaine lettuce wedge, chicken cube, and Parmesan cheese cube onto each toothpick, respectively. Arrange toothpicks on a serving platter and drizzle Caesar salad dressing over each.
